---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import siteContent from '../../content/site.en.json';

const lang = 'en';
---

<MainLayout
  title={`ForceField Scanner Terms | ${siteContent.company}`}
  description="ForceField Scanner Terms — the terms governing your use of the ForceField Scanner for AI security testing."
  lang={lang}
>
  <Header lang={lang} content={siteContent} />
  
  <main>
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary-900 to-secondary-800 py-16">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-primary-500/20 text-primary-400 text-sm font-medium mb-6">
            <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
            Legal
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">ForceField Scanner Terms</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-secondary-300">
            Terms governing the use of the ForceField Scanner for AI security testing.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
          
          <div class="mb-8 p-6 rounded-xl bg-primary-50 dark:bg-primary-900/20 border border-primary-200 dark:border-primary-800">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary-500 text-white flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm text-secondary-600 dark:text-secondary-400">
                  <strong class="text-secondary-900 dark:text-white">Last Updated:</strong> March 15, 2026<br />
                  <strong class="text-secondary-900 dark:text-white">Legal Entity:</strong> 9558-6616 Qu&eacute;bec Inc.<br />
                  <strong class="text-secondary-900 dark:text-white">Version fran&ccedil;aise :</strong> <a href="/fr/conditions-scanner" class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline">Conditions du Scanner ForceField</a>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
            
            <div class="not-prose mb-10 p-6 rounded-xl bg-secondary-900 dark:bg-secondary-800 text-white">
              <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" />
                </svg>
                Overview
              </h2>
              <p class="text-secondary-300 mb-0">
                The ForceField Scanner is designed for passive AI security testing. It performs prompt-level and behavior-level analysis of AI systems and does not conduct infrastructure penetration testing.
              </p>
            </div>

            <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-900 dark:text-white">1. Authorization</h2>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 dark:text-secondary-300">
              Users confirm they own or have explicit authorization to test any system submitted to the ForceField Scanner. You must not use the scanner to test systems belonging to third parties without their written consent.
            </p>

            <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-900 dark:text-white">2. Scope of Testing</h2>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 dark:text-secondary-300">
              The scanner performs prompt-level and behavior-level analysis of AI systems. Scans are performed against the ForceField Gateway detection pipeline and do not directly interact with your production systems. The scanner does not conduct infrastructure penetration testing, network scanning, or exploit execution.
            </p>

            <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-900 dark:text-white">3. Data Processing</h2>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 dark:text-secondary-300">
              The scanner processes prompts submitted for analysis, scanned URLs or endpoint identifiers, vulnerability results, and logs and timestamps for rate-limiting and abuse prevention. See the <a href="/en/scanner-privacy" class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline">Scanner Privacy Addendum</a> for full details.
            </p>

            <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-900 dark:text-white">4. Rate Limiting</h2>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 dark:text-secondary-300">
              ForceField reserves the right to rate-limit or suspend scanner access for abuse, excessive automated usage, or violations of these terms.
            </p>

            <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-900 dark:text-white">5. Governing Law</h2>
            <div class="mt-4 rounded-lg bg-secondary-100 p-6 dark:bg-secondary-800">
              <p class="text-secondary-900 dark:text-white">
                These Scanner Terms are governed by the <strong>laws of the Province of Qu&eacute;bec, Canada</strong> and are subject to the <a href="/en/terms" class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline">ForceField Platform Terms</a>.
              </p>
            </div>

            <p class="mt-8 text-secondary-500 dark:text-secondary-500 text-sm">
              &copy; 9558-6616 Qu&eacute;bec Inc.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer lang={lang} content={siteContent} />
</MainLayout>
